column5: It was in Oakville nippising.
Looks like a good time was had by all! Thanks for posting some pics so the rest of us could see what we missed.  Whopper

Thankyou Carp that was very sweet of you to say.  Yes it is most certainly a passion for me when it comes to fishing.  As for the funny look......lol Well everyone that knows me knows all i love to do is fish...& i thought well we are at a meet & greet with people who love to fish......Just threw me off gaurd i guess.......lol.......   You and your lady are great and hope too meet up again sometime in the near future. I never asked but does ur wife fish?

Although the pics lead you to believe we were the life of the party.. we really weren't. I guess we were all too tired to be our hyper, attention hogging selves. I think most of the people there will be grateful they didnt see the Filthwich Boyz in their full bloom.  Did I mention that Sleded is BALD?!
Nothing wrong with being or going bald.  Sledded your looking pretty RUFF!!! In that pic. lol
LOL, I would have looked worse than sled if I had made it there.  Thanks for the swill report.  LOL, I would have looked worse than sled if I had made it there.  Thanks for the swill report.
You have one to many last night Tjsa?....lol

Well 1st off let me say i had an absolute blast tonight and it was great to finally meet some fellow ofnr's. It was kinda weird though everyone knew who i was a few of you i did reconize some i did not....lol... As rich allready said they showed up at my place while i had actually just got out the shower. For some reason josh felt he had to grope my poor santa speaking of which fishergrl is now known as groper. Long story....LOL.......I have alot of pictures but thought i would add a few now. Not sure some are suitable for this forum lol..... ' 1st picture is of myself and Mr Arron and lemme tell ya i got a good chuckle when he asked me if i fished....LOL.......That was just too funny...    2nd picture is of myself Again Mr arron and BBR.   3RD PICTURE IS OF MYSELF AND FISHERGRL now known as groper......LOL   Myself and joey   The four of us groper,joey myself and speil.....I think if speil had had his own way we would have been stood there for another hr havin pics taken, lol   This next picture is of Carp.....lol..   Another pictute of groper carp myself and fishindevil. I love this picture.    Next picture is groper arron and myself.   I have lots more pics to come....joey it was great finally meeting you as it was everyone else...Fishergrl i had such a larf i honeslty cannot remember the last time i larfed so much my sides actually hurt.  Arron,roger,speil,carp misty river and wifes great meeting you all also...Sorry if i left out any names but there were quiet a few of you and hard to remember everyones names. I enjoyed the swill and hopefully will get to hook up with some of you in the new yr for a fish.   Nautifish.
....Nice shots Nautifish.    Glad to see you got those young'ns home okay....lol Was a pleasure meeting you and the crew from PD.
Looks like quite a party.
Looks a good time for all, thanks for the pic's...
Super pics... and of course it was a good time...  we collect the best!! (and watch out for the Spiel dude...)

lol speil.......Yeah i swear these boy's are like an extension of my family. I have two lads out on they're own only one left at home but some how i ended up with these three also.....Nice thing is though i can kick there tookishes back home.........  This was the boy's on the way home last night. I was thinking it was to quiet in the back which trust me when you get these three lads togeather its just not normal lol  & this is what i saw......It was heavenly bliss.    Speil great meeting you also.....   and watch out for the Spiel dude...) I don't doubt that for a second TJ.....lol
Hahahahaha!!!   I like the image name...3littlepiggysallfastasleep.jpg  Just be thankful they were sleeping I guess....

LOL TJ Bad aint i or maybe i should say Nauti.....lol  Fishergrl aka now known as groper....LOL I got ur pm i guess  a couple of the guy's took care of it so now rich is on a promise to donate. Otherwise i really will beat his (_)_).  Fishergrl had a blast last night and thanx.  I will be back later to post alot more pics right now i am heading back out the door to go fishing.
It is so good to hear that everything went smoothly  I had a blast too. We have to get together again sometime

LMFO... Love the report and Pic's NautiFish...  Wish I could have been there, but had a 2:30 am wake up call for WORK...grrr and couldn't make it... I sure am enjoying the reports while I sit through my lunch break today.....  Thanks for sharing...
Nice report Nautifish.  It was nice to meet you.
hi everyone it was sure fun meeting all of you  ,we had alot of fun and the wings were great,  cant wait to do it again   cheers

A swell swill last night.  It was nice to see so many familiar faces and a few new ones.  Some great pics nautifish. Quite the dynamic duo yourself and fishergirl were. Groper ? I was wondering who's hand that was.  We had a nice chat. You seem to have a passion for fishing that would rival anyone on this board and you're a classy lady as well. It was funny to see the expression on your face when people asked if you like to fish.  Thanks for keeping an eye on those young bucks too.  Your posts are great, so keep them coming.

Great pictures Nautifish.  It was great to meet some other "fishergals" and shoot the bull for awhile.  I think everyone had a great time, myself included (some more than others   )  I have a few pics I'll post in a bit.  Great seeing everyone again and meeting a few I hadn't yet.  Cheers.  Joey
Please excuse my ignorance but where did all this action take place?
Glad to see you all had yourselves a great time !!!! Wish I could of been there  Cheers !!!

There was a big get-together last night at the Firehall, one of the traditional OFC get-togethers (a.k.a. the Christmas swill).  I haven't made it to one yet, thought I was going yesterday but have been feeling run down and didn't think a late night with beer & wings would do me any good...      Mike

It was great to see some of you again and meet some new faces as well.  The swill was a lot of fun.. hard to beat chicken wings and beer and talk fishing with everyone.  Oh yeah.. and I know why you go by the name of 'Nauti' and 'groper' now  Have a great New Years everyone!  Aaron

i had a good time it was nice to meet you all. NautiFish... do u fish?? ha ha ha! I was soo tired but thats what happends when u fish all day in the wind and cold then come home an fillet fish then get ready to go lol!!!

Lady walley would have been great to meet ya maybe next time.....Funnt thing is us grls were trying to think of how many females actually had there pics posted on this site and i think we totalled five all togeather. You being in that five but we could not remember your name i said i just remember you being on the ice holding a fish....lol....  And arron me Nauti?...NOWAY!!!   Fishergrl yes very much so.....lol  & Fishergrl we certainly do need to get togeather again....I think in the new year we need to organize a weekend fishing trip for the grls only.
LOL, Hey I was good last night.   and that wasn't my hand.LMFO   I hope that nickname does not stick for too long, LOL
Ohhh trust me its gonna stick///////   I'LL MAKE SURE OF THAT
LMFO, thank you very much Nautifish Groper, there now you can have one too! LOL

Hi Nautifish..Looks like you all had a pretty good time last night. I asked earlier today where this occasion happened. The reply I seen was the firehall. We have a firehall in my town too..  ..I will guess somewhere in the vicinity of Toronto?  Keep up the fun...
